	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rem omnem ab ovo, ut aiunt, Troiano <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8083">Fortmüllerus</persName> noster orsus dissidii fontem aperire tibi voluit, quo plane intelligeres, cur tot annis iratum habuerit <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p8071">Aucupem</persName>, sic enim vocat <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p8071">Voglerum</persName> nostrum.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non legi, quae mihi concredidit tuo nomine petiitque, ut ad te bona fide curarem perferenda.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At vero, quoniam totum argumentum plus quam tragicum esse ex ipsius ore intellexi, valde consultum mihi videtur, amantissime vir, ut nihil horum resciscat <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8071" cert="high">Voglerus</persName> ac ne <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2815">Rordorfius</persName> quidem omnia, qui paulo est <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8071" cert="high">Voglero</persName> coniunctior, quam ut ipsi haec penitius quam a vestibulo intueri liceat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego quicquid possum ad sopiendam seu, ut recte dicam, tillendam tot annis grassantem simultatem, bona fide praestabo nec ambigo, quin me sit auditurus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8083">Fortmüllerus</persName>; tantum curato, ut et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8071" cert="high">Aucuparius</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8071" cert="high">Vogler</persName>.</note> te audiat tibique obsecundet pie et christiano animo admonenti.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeteriit ille, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8071" cert="high">Vogleri</persName> spe pacificandi, tuum nomen mihique historiam dedit velut ad <persName type="auto_name">Michaelem</persName> quendam scriptam, quam ego manu <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8083">Fortmülleri</persName> exaratam ad te mittam.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Petit autem, ut vel <foreign xml:lang="el">[griechisch]</foreign> remittas vel descriptum mittas exemplum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2815">Rordorphio</persName> me perquam libenter impertiissem quantuliscunque officiis, sed maiora fuere negocia eius, quam ut locus mihi ullus dari potuerit.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Virum arbitror certe optimum et humanissimum, cui sum equidem ad gratificandum promptus paratusque.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l474" cert="high">Sangalli</placeName>, sexto calendas Maias, anno etc. XLVIII.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Ioachimus Vadianus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, amico spectatissimo suo.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Lege chartam hanc cooperientem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8083">Fortmülleri</persName> literas.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
